Add __ppc64__ and __arm__
Recognize __sun as well as sun
Add __ia64__
Also recognize __sparc__ apparently now needed for gcc49 on solaris sparc
to avoid -M /usr/lib/ld/map.noexdata which in does not work on SPARC

